			where="Oracle" 
			when="Sep 2023 - Oct 2024" 
			title="Senior Software Engineer"
			list=`	Led the migration of 40+ legacy RESTful microservices from AWS to OCI.
					Standardised CI/CD workflows across projects, reducing maintenance time.
					Architected a polyglot persistence design in Java, reducing latency from 20s to 100ms.
					Optimized core database schema, reducing CPU, memory, and disk I/O by 90%.
					Designed a distributed event-driven data-sync system using Kafka.
					Mentored engineers on distributed system architectures and design patterns.`/>
			<Role 
			where="Oracle" 
			when="Aug 2021 - Sep 2023" 
			title="Software Engineer"
			list=`	Enabled cloud provider hot-swapping in Go with Strategy Pattern.
					Solved high latency, remediating bottlenecks in 1 GB/s traffic with Worker pattern.
					Used layered patterns to ensure simple and consistent design of React Components.
					Led UI development across organisation using React, TypeScript and Webpack.
					Mentored engineers on modern front-end development, guiding them through responsive design principles.`/>
			<Role 
			where="Amazon Prime Air" 
			when="Jul 2019 - Apr 2020" 
			title="SDE II"
			list=`	Replaced 1hr video pipeline, with a Python script saving each person 3 hours per day.
					Architected a distributed media cache eliminating 30Gbps bandwidth bottleneck.
					Swapped video review tools saving 75,000 hours annually.
					Contributed in technical discussions with Engineers and Management.`/>
		</div>

		<!-- {fonts.split(", ").map(font => <Fonts name={font}/>)} -->


		</div>
	</main>
